üî• CCEE POWER MEMORY (HIGH-YIELD)
SSE-CMM = Security Engineering Maturity Model
Focus = HOW well security is engineered, not just WHAT controls exist
Pilots = Proof of practical applicability
Low maturity = Ad-hoc | High maturity = Predictable & optimized
